\name{tccquickr-package}
\alias{tccquickr-package}
\alias{tccquickr}
\title{Experimental R-to-C Lowering on Top of Rtinycc}
\description{
The \pkg{tccquickr} package contains the experimental \code{tcc_quick()}
front-end and its supporting parser, IR, lowering, and code-generation
layers. It is intended to sit on top of \pkg{Rtinycc}, which provides the
TinyCC runtime, FFI bindings, and low-level compilation pipeline.
}
